---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About ProxyFAQs | The Stack Overflow for Proxies" description="Learn about ProxyFAQs, the vendor-neutral knowledge platform for proxy and web scraping questions.">
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50 to-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">
        About ProxyFAQs
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        The Stack Overflow for proxies - your vendor-neutral knowledge platform
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <!-- Mission -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        ProxyFAQs is built to solve a simple problem: finding reliable, vendor-neutral information about proxies is hard.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Today, developers and businesses waste hours searching through:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li>Outdated blog posts from 2018</li>
        <li>Reddit threads with conflicting advice</li>
        <li>Vendor marketing materials disguised as guides</li>
        <li>Scattered forum discussions across dozens of sites</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        We're building the definitive knowledge hub where you can find answers to 1M+ questions,
        compare providers with real data, and get instant help from an AI trained on 10 years of proxy expertise.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What Makes Us Different</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Vendor Neutral</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We're not owned by any proxy provider. Our recommendations are based on real data and community feedback,
            not who pays us the most.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Data-Driven</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Every answer is backed by real-world data. We've analyzed 1M+ questions people actually ask Google
            about proxies and web scraping.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI-Powered</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Our AI chat assistant is trained on 10 years of proxy expertise. It understands your specific use case
            and provides contextual recommendations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Always Up-to-Date</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Proxy providers change their offerings constantly. We track pricing, features, and performance
            so you don't have to.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- For Whom -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Who We Serve</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Developers</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Software engineers building scrapers, bots, and data pipelines who need technical answers fast.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Businesses</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            E-commerce sellers, SEO agencies, and data companies who need reliable proxy solutions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Learners</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Students and hobbyists who want to understand proxies without getting lost in jargon.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Transparency -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Transparency</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We believe in full transparency about how we make money:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>Some provider links are affiliate links - we earn a commission if you sign up</li>
        <li>Affiliate status never affects our rankings or recommendations</li>
        <li>All affiliate links are clearly marked with a disclosure</li>
        <li>We only recommend providers we've personally tested or verified</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Open Source -->
    <div class="mb-12 bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Built in Public</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        ProxyFAQs is built using modern web technologies:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>Astro 4.x for lightning-fast static generation</li>
        <li>Supabase PostgreSQL for our knowledge base</li>
        <li>VectorEngine API (grok-4-fast) for AI chat</li>
        <li>Cloudflare Pages for global edge delivery</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        We're committed to building the best proxy knowledge platform in the world.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Have questions, suggestions, or want to partner with us?
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/search"
          class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
        >
          Browse Questions
        </a>
        <a
          href="/providers"
          class="bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium border border-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"
        >
          Compare Providers
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
